entries.s_12: You look very centered. I take it you found what you were searching for?
entries.s_13: Yes. I found a suitable crystal.
entries.s_14: It will be useful to you. Nos'lyn sent this to me for you. It's his first lightsaber. I'd be careful who you wave it in front of, but it should serve you well.
entries.s_15: Ah, you are on the next step, already? Very good. I will look forward to speaking with you when you are done.
entries.s_17: Nos'lyn thinks that you are doing well. You will be ready for the next step of your journey soon.
entries.s_20: I am. How did you know?
entries.s_22: Nos'lyn informed me of your arrival. He said that you are a very promising pupil. I can see what he means.
entries.s_24: Of course I am! How could you not know me?
entries.s_26: Hmmm. Nos'lyn may be wrong about you. Perhaps there is not greatness so much as pride. Either way, I have something for you.
entries.s_28: Hello.  It's a lovely day today, isn't it?
